  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the fondue pot to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Place the confit tomatoes, olive oil, balsamic vinegar, garlic, salt, and black pepper in the fondue pot.",
    "Stir in the grated Parmesan cheese until melted and well combined.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Stir in chopped parsley and serve immediately.",
    "Serve the confit tomato mixture in the fondue pot with crusty bread or crackers for dipping.",
    "Garnish with additional parsley if desired.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
